{
  "title": "Deliciously Crisp Venezuelan Chinese Cabbage Skewers",
  "description": "A fermented and crisp Venezuelan dish featuring Chinese cabbage, perfect for a lazy Sunday, and diabetic-friendly. This recipe combines the flavors of Venezuela with the crunch of Chinese cabbage.",
